            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "My use case is that sometimes I want to disable all lsp/lint/highlighting stuff and just quickly edit the text (for example, a large json file). My quick and dirty solution was to unset the filetype (`:set ft=`). This does however not disable the LSP.\n\n(I now noticed that this also doesn't disable treesitter, just its highlighting)",
